\imt1 N…ôgkiarien kwakw…ô kape n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e Revelesen  
\ip \bd ?Pa r…®m…®rai n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e?\bd* Aposol Jon r…®m…®rai n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e. In piau Jemes, k…®ni iriu ji Sepedi mir. Jon, in yermam…ô twelef k…®rik kape Yesu, k…®ni Yesu rorkeikei p…®k in. N…ôkw…ôkw…ô yam…ô m…®n…ô e Jon r…®m…®rai, nhagri…ô e: N…ôvsaoyen Huv…ô yame Jon r…®m…®rai, m…®ne 1 Jon, m…®ne 2 Jon, m…®ne 3 Jon, m…®ne Revelesen.  
\ip \bd ?R…®m…®rai ramv…ôn k…®mi n…®pa?\bd* In r…®m…®rai n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e ramv…ôn k…®mi nim…ôhuak seven yam…ô m…®ne kas…ôrer ye provins a Tarki, mamv…ôn m…®n k…®mi nim…ôhuak m…®n…ô fam.  
\ip \bd ?Nar…ôyen r…®mnhawor p…ôn iran m…®ne ye n…®p…®g r…®m…®rai?\bd* N…®p…®g a yame r…®m…®rai n…ôkw…ôkw…ô iran, gavman kape Rom ramni m…®m…ô narmam…ô tukas…ôkeikei mas…ôhuak k…®mi yemehu…ô kape gavman ramhen k…®n kughen kap…ôri…ô. M…ôr…®g n…ôm…ôhuak m…®n…ô kham…ô yermam…ô k…®rikian…ô …ôm…ô in yerp…®r…®g …ôgk…ôp. Yermam…ô e in Yesu Kristo. In p…®s…®n …ôm…ô in Yermaru. Ror m…ôkneik…®n, gavman kape Rom ramor ahas p…ôn k…®mi n…ôm…ôhuak m…®n…ô. Jon in yamehu…ô k…®rik ye nim…ôhuak, kher-yerhav k…®n ruv…ôn isok, apa kwaji tan…ô e kamni k…®m…ô Patmos m…ô tukramar…ô in p…®s…®n …ôm…ô. Aik…®n, Kughen r…®v…ôhsi-p…ôn n…ômr…ôrhavyen k…®min, m…ô tukr…ôm Yesu Kristo apa ye rao ye neai. K…®ni m…ôm m…®n nar…®mnar yam…ô m…®ne tukr…®piu…ô. Iri…ô e: Kughen tukrapita ye narowag…®nien yame narmam…ô m…®ne Setan tuksor iri…ô min. K…®ni Kughen tukr…ôkir narmam…ô m-fam ye N…®p…®g Kwas…®g.  
\ip \bd ?R…®m…®rai n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e tuk naha? \bd* In r…®m…®rai n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e m…ô tukror …ôpu m…ô Yesu Kristo in Yermaru, k…®ni mhajoun kafan n…ôsan…®nien. K…®ni in rorkeikei m…ô tukr…®ni-p…ôn tuk n…ôm…ôhuak m…®n…ô m…ô tuks…ôrer t…®m t…®m tukm…ô n…®p…®g …ôut…ôn ru…ô tuk …ôri…ô, k…®ni p…ôh tukhap…ôh n…®s…ôhuakien k…®mi yemehu…ô kape gavman kape Rom r…ômhen k…®n kughen kap…ôri…ô. P…ôh nien m…ô tuktu, Setan tukror ahas p…ôn k…®mi n…ôm…ôhuak m…®n…ô, m…ôr…®g iri…ô tukas…ôkeikei mas…ôrer t…®mt…®m. K…®ni Jon rorkeikei m…ô tukr…®v…ôh-si hakt…ô n…ôr…®gien kape n…ôm…ôhuak m…®n…ô m…®ne narmam…ô e kasar…ô ye n…®p…®g …ôut…ôn ai takt…ôkun. N…®p…®g Yesu Kristo tukr…®rer…®g-p…ô m…®n iran, k…®ni In tukr…®-v…ôhsihakt…ô …ôri…ô.  
