\v 12 K…®ni, y…®mnarar m…ô jak…ôm-ru m…ô pa e ram…ôgkiar k…®mi yo. Marar, m…ôm nar k…®rik k…ôr…ôhu-p…ôn laet iran, iri…ô fam seven. K…®mnor k…®n gol.\fig Nar k…®rik k…ôr…ôhu-p…ôn laet iran iri…ô fam seven|alt="lampstands" src="HK018E.jpg" size="col" copy="Horace Knowles" ref="Rev 1:12" \fig*  
