\v 18 Yo e yem…ô mragh.\x - \xo 1:18 \xt Sam 42:2\x* !Y…®mamh…ô mokup…ôn m…ôr…®g, …ôm-ru, yakamragh rer…®n! K…®ni yo yakamehu…ô ye n…®mh…ôyen; yak…®rkun n…ôhit…ôyen ye kw…ônmhaan kape n…®mh…ôyen.  
