\c 2  
\s1 N…ôgkiarien ramv…ôn k…®mi n…ôm…ôhuak m…®n…ô apa Efesas  
\p
\v 1 K…®ni r…®m…®ni-p…ô tuk yo m…®m…ô ‚ÄúRai n…ôkw…ôkw…ô k…®rik r…®v…ôn k…®mi agelo kape nim…ôhuak apa taon e Efesas, m…®ni-p…ôn m…®m…ô, \fig Nim…ôhuak iri…ô m-fam seven|alt="Places where the seven churches were" src="7 Churches.jpg" size="span" loc="Between chap 1 & 2" ref="REV 2:1" \fig*  
\pi1 Yermam…ô yame rav…ôh k…ômhau seven ye kwerm…®n matuk,\x - \xo 2:1 \xt Rev 1:16\x* mameriw…ôk ye kwerkwan ye nar kam…ôr…ôhu-p…ôn laet iran,\x - \xo 2:1 \xt Rev 1:12-13\x* iri…ô seven, yame k…®mnor k…®n gol, kafan e n…ôgkiarien ramni m…®m…ô,   
