\v 4 M…ôr…®g nakasor nar k…®rik yame rap…ôh n…ômhenien ye n…®mr…®k: Nakw…ôs…ôp…ôh norkeikeiyen kup…ôn kap…ômi…ô.\x - \xo 2:4 \xt Jon 13:35; Jer 2:2-5\x*  
