\s1 Kas…ôgn…ôg…®n Kughen ye rao ye neai  
\p
\v 1 Kwas…®g ik…®n, y…®m…®waag hakt…ô m…ôm kw…ôru…ô k…®rik ram…ôkwag apa ye neai. K…®ni y…®mn…ôr…®g m…®n yermam…ô yame r…®nam…ôgkiar k…®mi yo kup…ôn. Ram…ôgkiar m…®n k…®mi yo, r…®kin rehu…ô r…ômhen k…®n naiyuk, m…®m…ô ‚ÄúHek…®mter, mu…ô. Yakhajoun ik k…®n nar…®mnar yam…ô m…®ne tukr…®piu…ô.‚Äù  
\v 2 M…ôkneik…®n, n…ôsan…®nien kape Nanm…®n Rhak…ô r…®mnor k…®mi yo. Yakwaag kup…ôn, m…ôm King ramkw…ôt…ô ye jea kafan, mamarmaru ye rao ye neai.\x - \xo 4:2 \xt Esik 1:26-28\x*  
\v 3 K…®ni yermam…ô yame ramkw…ôt…ô aik…®n a, yak…ôm in rhuv…ô m…ôrir, r…ômhen k…®n kapier huv…ô mir k…®raru nhagriu e jaspa m…®ne kanilian. K…®ni m…ôrai-m…ôrai k…®rik rarkurao ye jea kafan, mam…ôsi…ô p…®k r…ômhen k…®n kapier huv…ô e emeral.  
\v 4 K…®ni jea t…®ks…®n aik…®n, iri…ô m-fam 24, kasarkurao ye jea ehu…ô a kape King. K…®ni namehu…ô t…®ks…®n, iri…ô m-fam 24, kas…ôkw…ôt…ô-p…ôn ye jea m…®n…ô a; mhav…ôhsi-p…ôn neip…ôn haw…ôn, m…®s…ôv…ôvhao k…®n k…ôv…ôvhao kape n…®siaiyen, k…®mnor k…®n gol.  
\v 5 K…®ni ik…®n a, jea kape king ram…ôrer ik…®n, ramaroap…®g, nuvr…®g-uvr…®gien ramav…ôn, k…®ni karu…ôru…ô ram…ôrkw…ôm…ôtei mamt…ôrhav. K…®ni kup…ôn ye jea laet iri…ô seven kamhau…ôk. In a Nanm…®n kape Kughen, iri…ô seven.  
\v 6 In a kup…ôn ye jea kape king, nar k…®rik aik…®n r…ômhen k…®n tahik, m…ôr…®g r…ômhen k…®n glas yame r…ôrir mam…ôsi…ô.  
\p K…®ni in a ye kwerkwan, nar m…®ragh m…®n…ô, kamni k…®m…ô ‚Äújerubim,‚Äù iri…ô kuas, kasarkurao ye jea ehu…ô kape King. N…®mr…®ri…ô r…®psaah p…®k, mamswin-p…ôn apnap…®g …ôm…ô ye n…®prairi…ô m…®ne n…®meitairi…ô.  
\v 7 Yame kup…ôn ik…®n, r…ômhen k…®n laeon. Yame ror k…®raru k…®n, r…ômhen k…®n kau. Yame ror k…®sis…ôr k…®n, kap…ôn kap…ô r…ômhen k…®n yermam…ô. K…®ni yame ror kuas k…®n, r…ômhen k…®n kweri…ô yame ravi…ô.  
\v 8 Nar m…®ragh m…®n…ô a kuas, t…ôm…ôr-…ôm…ôr…®ri…ô sikis. K…®ni n…®mr…®ri…ô ramswin-p…ôn apnap…®g …ôm…ô ir…ôri…ô, m…®v…ôn ye t…®k…®rk…ôv…®ri…ô. N…®p…®g m-fam kas…ôni n…®pei, yenp…®g m…®ne yeraan, mhap…ôh nhap…ôhyen, mamhani mham…ô,  
\q1 ‚ÄúKughen Yermaru, Nagheen Rehu…ô P…®k.  
