\q1 In r…®namar…ô rer…®n, mamar…ô ai takt…ôkun, tukr…®piar…ô rer…®n m…®n.‚Äù\x - \xo 4:8 \xt Eks 3:14\x*   
\p
\v 9 K…®ni nar m…®ragh m…®n…ô a, kamhani n…ôfrak…®sien ye nehu…ôyen kape Kughen, mamhav…ôhsi-p…ôn n…®siaiyen k…®min, mamhani vi vi King yame ramkw…ôt…ô-p…ôn ye jea, mamarmaru mamar…ô rer…®n, infamien r…®rk…ôk.  
\v 10 Iri…ô kamhani vi vi In, n…ômehu…ô m…®n…ô, iri…ô m-fam 24, kas…ôn…®mkur ye n…®hu yermam…ô a yame ramkw…ôt…ô-p…ôn ye jea, mamarmaru, mamar…ô rer…®n, infamien r…®rk…ôk, mas…ôgn…ôg…®n In. Kw…ôs…ôv…ôvhao k…®n k…ôv…ôvhao kape king, m…ôkneik…®n, mhar…ôhsi-ta, m…®s…ôr…ôhu kup…ôn ye jea yame King ramkw…ôt…ô ik…®n mamarmaru, mamhani mham…ô,   
\q1
\v 11 ‚ÄúKap…ômaw…ô Yermaru Kughen,  
\q2 Ik nakatuatuk m…ômhen …ôgk…ôp m…ô narmam…ô m-fam tuks…ôgn…ôg…®n …ôm…ô Ik, mhasiai …ôm…ô Ik, meinai Ik n…®mnor nar…®mnar m-fam. Nagheem rehu…ô p…®k.  
\q1 N…®mn…ôgkiar …ôm…ô m…®ni m…ô nar…®mnar m-fam tukhaswin, m…ôkneik…®n kamhaswin …ôfrak…®s mamhamragh.‚Äù   
\c 5  
\s1 Kwaji sipsip ram…ôvi n…ôkw…ôkw…ô yame k…®mnarp…ôv…®n  
\p
\v 1 M…ôkneik…®n, y…®mn…ôm King ramkw…ôt…ô-p…ôn ye kafan jea, m…®v…ôh n…ôkw…ôkw…ô yame k…®mnarp…ôv…®n-arp…ôv…®n ye kwerm…®n matuk. K…®m…®rai-p…ôn n…ôgkiarien ye n…®kar…®n mir. K…®vaan kandel raiyu, k…®vaan …ôt…ôr…ôk…®n ye n…ôp…ô…ôg n…®mr…®n m-seven.\fig K…®vaan kandel raiyu, k…®vaan …ôt…ôr…ôk…®n n…ôkw…ôkw…ô yame k…®mnarp…ôv…®n-arp…ôv…®n|alt="Unopened book sealed with seven wax seals" src="Scroll_d.jpg" size="col" loc="Near verse" copy="Urs Wegmann" ref="REV 5:1" \fig*  
\v 2 M…ôkneik…®n y…®mn…ôm agelo …ôsan…®n k…®rik ram…ôgkiar p…®k mamaiyoh m…®m…ô, ‚Äú?Pa e in r…ômhen matuatuk m…ô to r…ôv…®t-…ôp…®r-p…®r nehe kandel, m…ôvi n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e?‚Äù  
\v 3 M…ôr…®g yermam…ô k…®rik r…®rk…ôk ye rao ye neai, u…ô tokrei tan…ô, u…ô ye kw…ônmhaan kape n…®mh…ôyen, yame in ratuatuk m…ô to r…ôvi n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e m…ôvheik…®n.  
\v 4 Yermam…ô r…®rk…ôk yame ratuatuk m…ô to r…ôvi n…ôkw…ôkw…ô m…ôhuek…®n, yakas…ôk p…®k tukun.  
\v 5 K…®ni ai, yemehu…ô k…®rik r…®m…®ni-p…ô tuk yo m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúP…ôh nas…ôkien. ∆ém-ru, Kw…ôn e kamni k…®m…ô, ‚ÄòLaeon kape kw…ôn…ôr…ôus kape Judah,‚Äô\x - \xo 5:5 \xt Jen 49:9-10\x* in Nukne Deved,\x - \xo 5:5 \xt Aes 11:1\x* in r…®napita ta ye narowag…®nien kafan. K…®ni in ratuatuk m…ô to rakap…®r nehe kandel seven, m…ôvi n…ôkw…ôkw…ô a.‚Äù   
\p
\v 6 M…ôkneik…®n, y…®mn…ôm kwaji sipsip k…®rik ram…ôrer ye kwerkwan ye jea kape King m…®ne nar m…®ragh kuas e, kamni k…®m…ô ‚Äòjerubim,‚Äô m…®ne namasur m…®n…ô iri…ô 24. Nak…ôm Kwaji Sipsip a nakm…ôta m…ô k…®nhopni-ta. Kapan …ôpat seven, k…®ni n…®mr…®n, iri…ô seven m…®n, iri…ô a kas…ôrer tuk nanm…®n kape Kughen iri…ô seven, yam…ô m…®ne r…®mnher-p…ô k…®n …ôri…ô kamhav…ôn ye tan…®mtan…ô.  
\v 7 Kwaji Sipsip e, r…®v…ôn a ik…®n King ramkw…ôt…ô-p…ôn ye kafan jea ik…®n, m…ôrao-p…ôn m…®r…ôhsi-ta n…ôkw…ôkw…ô ye kwerm…® King matuk.  
\v 8 M…®r…ôhsi-ta ta n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e, m…ôkneik…®n, nar m…®ragh m…®n…ô, iri…ô kuas, kamni k…®m…ô ‚Äòjerubim,‚Äô m…®ne namasur, iri…ô m-fam 24, kas…ôn…®mkur ye n…®hu Kwaji Sipsip. K…®mnhav…ôh gita\f + \fr 5:8 \ft  N…ôgkiarien kape n…ôm…ô Gris rap…ôh n…®niyen ‚Äògita,‚Äô mamni …ôm…ô ‚Äòhap.‚Äô In nar k…®rik kamuh tuk n…ôniyen n…®pe, r…ômhen k…®n gita.\f* kap…ôri…ô, m…®ne besin k…®mnor k…®n gol, rukwar k…®n nar k…®rik yame ram…ônah, mapien huv…ô. K…®ni nar a ram…ônah mapien huv…ô in r…ômhen k…®n n…ôhuakien kape narmam…ô kape Kughen m…®n…ô.\x - \xo 5:8 \xt Sam 141:2\x*   
\p
\v 9 K…®ni nar m…®ragh m…®n…ô kuas e, kamni k…®m…ô ‚Äòjerubim,‚Äô m…®ne namasur m…®n…ô iri…ô 24, kas…ôni n…®pei vi k…®rik mham…ô,  
\q1 ‚ÄúIk nakatuatuk m…ômhen m…ô to nakv…ôh n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e,  
