\v 11 K…®ni y…®m…®waag-p…ôn m…®n m…ôm, m…ôr…®g r…®ki agelo m…®n…ô khapsaah khapsaah khapsaah, to k…®p…ôh n…ôhueik…®n-famien …ôri…ô. Kas…ôrer m…®sarkurao ye jea kape King m…®ne nar m…®ragh m…®n…ô e, kamni k…®m…ô, ‚Äòjerubim,‚Äô m…®ne n…ômasur m…®n…ô.  
\v 12 Kas…ôni p…®k n…®pei k…®rik mamhani mham…ô,  
\q1 ‚ÄúKwaji Sipsip yame k…®mnhopni, In ratuatuk m…ômhen m…ô tukhav…ôh-si hakt…ô In, meinai In rav…ôh fam n…ôsan…®nien, m…®ne n…®rkunien, m…®ne naut…ô, m…®ne nagheen. !P…ôh khasiai In, m…®s…ôgn…ôg…®n In!‚Äù   
\p
\v 13 M…ôkneik…®n, y…®mn…ôr…®g nar…®mnar fam yame Kughen r…®mnor ye rao ye neai, m…®ne ye tan…®mtan…ô, m…®ne ye tame tahik, m…®ne ye kw…ônmhaan kape n…®mh…ôyen, m…®ne nar…®mnar fam yame kamhaswin ir…ôri…ô, iri…ô m-fam kamhani mham…ô,  
\q1 ‚ÄúP…ôh n…®ni-vi-vi-yen m…®ne n…®siaiyen ramv…ôn tuk King yame ramkw…ôt…ô-p…ôn ye jea, m…®ne tuk Kwaji Sipsip, meinai In rav…ôh n…®khakien m…®ne narmaruyen.  
\q2 !P…ôh n…®ni-vi-vi-yen m…®ne n…ôsan…®nien ramv…ôn tuk …ôriu, m…®v…ôn, m…®v…ôn, m…®v…ôn, m…®p…ôh norien infamien!‚Äù   
\p
\v 14 M…ôkneik…®n, nar m…®ragh e, kamni k…®m…ô, ‚Äòjerubim,‚Äô iri…ô kuas, kamhani mham…ô, ‚Äú!Amen!‚Äù K…®ni n…ômehu…ô m…®n…ô k…®s…ôn…®mkur ye n…®hun, m…®s…ôgn…ôg…®n In.   
\c 6  
\s1 Kwaji sipsip r…ôv…®t-…ôp…®r-p…®r nehe kandel yame k…®m…®vaan-…ôt…ôr…ôk…®n n…ôkw…ôkw…ô k…®n  
\p
\v 1 K…®ni yak…ôm Kwaji Sipsip a r…ôv…®t-…ôp…®r-p…®r nehe kandel yame r…ôkup…ôn, yame k…®m…®vaan-…ôt…ôr…ôk…®n n…ôkw…ôkw…ô yame k…®mnarp…ôv…®n-arp…ôv…®n k…®n. M…ôkneik…®n, nar m…®ragh e kamni k…®m…ô, ‚Äòjerubim,‚Äô k…®rikian…ô ir…ôri…ô rarar mokr…ôn ehu…ô r…ômhen k…®n karu…ôru…ô, m…®m…ô, ‚Äú!Yu…ô-ru!‚Äù  
\v 2 Yakwaag hakt…ô m…ôm hos k…®rik khaw…ôn. Yermam…ô yame ramkw…ôt…ô ye hos ramr…ôh n…ôvhag…ô. M…ôkneik…®n k…ôv…ôvhao-p…ôn k…®n k…ôv…ôvhao k…®rik kape king iran. In ramaiyu mamav…ôn r…ômhen k…®n yermam…ô yame rapita ye narowag…®nien, k…®ni mamv…ôn m…®n m…ô tukrapita m…®n.   
\p
\v 3 K…®ni ai, Kwaji Sipsip a r…ôv…®t-…ôp…®r-p…®r nehe kandel yame k…®m…®vaan-…ôt…ôr…ôk…®n n…ôkw…ôkw…ô k…®n, yame ror k…®raru k…®n, k…®ni nar m…®ragh e kamni k…®m…ô ‚Äòjerubim,‚Äô yame ror k…®raru k…®n, rarar, mamni m…®m…ô, ‚Äú!Yu…ô-ru!‚Äù  
\v 4 M…ôkneik…®n, hos k…®rik k…ôwhao raiyu mu…ô. Yermam…ô yame ramkw…ôt…ô ye hos, k…®v…ôhsi-p…ôn nao kape narowag…®nien k…®min. K…®ni Kughen rameighan-p…ôn k…®n neihu…ôyen k…®min m…ô tukr…®r…ôhsita n…ôm…ôrinuyen ye tan…®mtan…ô. Nuhyen …ôjir ramav…ôn ik…®n m…®n…ô fam.   
\p
\v 5 K…®ni ai, Kwaji Sipsip a rakap…®r nehe kandel yame k…®m…®vaan-…ôt…ôr…ôk…®n n…ôkw…ôkw…ô k…®n, yame ror k…®sis…ôr k…®n, k…®ni nar m…®ragh e kamni k…®m…ô ‚Äòjerubim,‚Äô yame ror k…®sis…ôr k…®n, rarar, mamni m…®m…ô, ‚Äú!Yu…ô-ru!‚Äù M…ôkneik…®n, y…®m…®waag-p…ôn m…ôm hos k…®rik kap…®g. Yermam…ô yame ramkw…ôt…ô iran ramr…ôh skel k…®rik kape n…ôkirien n…ôv…®g…®nien.  
\v 6 K…®ni y…®mn…ôr…®g r…®ki yermam…ô k…®rik r…®s…®-p…ôn ye kwerkwan ye nar m…®ragh kuas e kamni k…®m…ô ‚Äòjerubim.‚Äô Mamni-p…ôn tukun m…®m…ô, ‚Äú!Yuv…ôn! Kameighan k…®n ik k…®m…ô takor n…®kumh…ô k…®mi tan…®mtan…ô. Tukm…ô k…®sarakik…®n mane ehu…ô mhav…ôh n…ôv…®g…®nien r…®k…ôsk…ôh …ôm…ô.\f + \fr 6:6 \ft  Gris ramni m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúN…®mr…® wit yame tukor bred k…®n kape n…®p…®g k…®rikian…ô …ôm…ô, n…®mr…®n rhakt…ô r…ômhen k…®n mane yame kam…ôrok tuk wok kape n…®p…®g k…®rikian…ô, k…®ni raes yame tuk…ôn ye n…®p…®g k…®rikian…ô, n…®p…®g rhakt…ô r…ômhen k…®n mane yame kam…ôrok tuk wok kape n…®p…®g k…®rikian…ô.‚Äù M…ôr…®g n…®pran e, tuksarakik…®n mane ehu…ô mhav…ôh n…ôv…®g…®nien r…®k…ôsk…ôh …ôm…ô.\f* M…ôr…®g takp…ôh noriahyen nuknei nai mir e kamni k…®m…ô ‚Äòolif,‚Äô m…®ne ‚Äògrep.‚Äô‚Äù   
\p
\v 7 K…®ni ai, Kwaji Sipsip a r…ôv…®t-…ôp…®r-p…®r nehe kandel yame k…®m…®vaan-…ôt…ôr…ôk…®n n…ôkw…ôkw…ô k…®n, yame ror kuas k…®n, k…®ni nar m…®ragh e kamni k…®m…ô ‚Äòjerubim,‚Äô yame ror kuas k…®n, rarar, mamni m…®m…ô, ‚Äú!Yu…ô-ru!‚Äù  
\v 8 Yakwaag-p…ôn m…ôm hos k…®rik k…ôrato. Yermam…ô yame ramkw…ôt…ô iran, nhag…®n e N…®mh…ôyen. Iriu kw…ôn k…®rik, nhag…®n e Kw…ônmhaan kape N…®mh…ôyen r…®kwas…®g k…®n in m…®rav…ôn. K…®r…ôv…ôh neihu…ôyen m…ô tukw…ôhapni narmam…ô k…®n nao, mwhopni …ôri…ô k…®n n…®kumh…ô, u…ô k…®n nar aparu m…®n…ô, u…ô k…®n n…ômh…ôyen. K…®r…ôv…ôh nehu…ôyen m…ôknak…®n r…ômhen k…®n n…®par n…®moptan…ô k…®rikian…ô, m…®r…ôp…ôh …ôm…ô n…®p…ôr…®n k…®sis…ôr.   
\p
\v 9 K…®ni ai, Kwaji Sipsip a r…ôv…®t-…ôp…®r-p…®r nehe kandel yame k…®m…®vaan-…ôt…ôr…ôk…®n n…ôkw…ôkw…ô k…®n, yame ror k…®rk…®r…®p k…®n, m…ôkneik…®n yakwaag-p…ôn ye n…ôp…ô…ôg tebol apa ye Nim…ô Ehu…ô kape Kughen, m…ôm narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne k…®mnhopni …ôri…ô tuk narer-t…®mt…®mien tuk n…®ni-…ôrhavyen n…ôgkiarien kape Kughen.  
\v 10 Iri…ô kasokr…ôn apomh mamhani-p…ôn tuk Kughen mham…ô, ‚ÄúIk nakamarmaru ye nar…®mnar m-fam. Ik nak…ôm…ôrhak…ô; k…®ni Ik n…ôfrak…®sien. ?M…ôr…®g, tuk nagheen m…®ne k…®ni Ik nak…ôkir narmam…ô ye tan…®mtan…ô, marp…®n tai n…®tawmaw…ô?‚Äù  
\v 11 Kamhani m…ôknak…®n, Kughen r…®v…ôhsi-p…ôn neip…ôn haw…ôn k…®mi …ôri…ô m-fam, m…®ni-p…ôn tuk …ôri…ô m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúTakhawhin pi pom. Piaumi…ô m…®n…ô m…®ne kak…ô kap…ômi…ô m…®n…ô t…®ks…®n kasor han…ô kafak wok. P…ôh k…®seriaji tukhopni pi…ôpi…ô m…®n narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne k…®m…®v…ôh n…®hup…®n ir…ôri…ô.‚Äù   
\p
\v 12 K…®ni ai, Kwaji Sipsip a r…ôv…®t-…ôp…®r-p…®r nehe kandel yame k…®m…®vaan-…ôt…ôr…ôk…®n n…ôkw…ôkw…ô k…®n, yame ror sikis k…®n, yak…ôm mig ehu…ô ramkiu. M…®rh r…®p…®s r…ôp…®gnap. Maku…ô r…ôwhao r…ômhen k…®n n…®t…ô.\x - \xo 6:12 \xt Joel 2:31; Wok 2:20\x*  
\v 13 K…ômhau m…®n…ô k…®s…ôsaah-…ôsaah m…®seiwaiyu-p…ô ye n…®moptan…ô, r…ômhen k…®n nai\f + \fr 6:13 \ft  Jon ramni nai k…®rik kamni k…®m…ô ‚Äòfigtri.‚Äô\f* yame n…®m…ôtag ehu…ô rameit…ôt…ôg k…®n, kw…ônkwan yame rapk…ôh r…ôsaah.  
\v 14 K…®ni neai r…®rk…ôk, r…ômhen k…®n yame k…®marp…ôv…®n-arp…ôv…®n fam t…ôvheit…ô.\x - \xo 6:14 \xt Aes 34:4\x* K…®ni tukwas m…®n…ô m…®ne tan…ô m…®n…ô k…®s…ôta ye kw…ônmhaan kap…ôri…ô m…®n…ô.   
\p
\v 15 K…®ni king m…®n…ô kape tan…®mtan…ô, m…®ne narmaru m…®n…ô, m…®ne namasur m…®n…ô kape mobael m…®n…ô, m…®ne narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne kap…ôri…ô naut…ô rehu…ô, m…®ne narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne kamhav…ôh nehu…ôyen, m…®ne slef m…®n…ô, m…®ne narmam…ô apnap…®g m…®n…ô, iri…ô m-fam khav…ôn m…®serkwaig ye n…ôp…ô…ôg kapier ehu…ô, u…ô kas…ôrer …ôtg…®n kapier m…®n…ô ye n…®kar tukwas m…®n…ô.\x - \xo 6:15 \xt Aes 2:10,19-22\x*  
\v 16 K…®ni k…®sas…ôk apomh-p…ôn tuk tukwas m…®n…ô m…®ne kapier ehu…ô m…®n…ô mham…ô, ‚Äú!∆ésaah! M…ôkw…ôt…ô-t…ôr…ôk…®n …ômaw…ô merkwaig k…®n …ômaw…ô ye n…®mr…® King e yame ramkw…ôt…ô ye kafan jea, m…®ne tuk niemhaa kape Kwaji Sipsip.\x - \xo 6:16 \xt Hos 10:8\x*  
\v 17 Meinai n…®p…®g a ruau…ô yame Kughen m…®ne Kwaji Sipsip tukrav…ôhsi-…ôrhav-p…ô niemhaa kap…ôriu. ?K…®ni pa nhag…®n r…®rkun narer-huv…ôyen?‚Äù\x - \xo 6:17 \xt Joel 2:11; Mal 3:2\x*   
\c 7  
\s1 K…®m…®rpen narmam…ô wan handred foti fo taosen m…ô kape Kughen  
\p
