\v 6 K…®ni yak…ôm m…ô piraov…®n a r…®nap…®s k…®n n…®taw narmam…ô kape Kughen m…®n…ô. Iri…ô e narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne k…®m…®sarer-…ôrhav tuk n…®ni-…ôrhavyen Yesu. Yak…ôm in, nanm…®k riv…ô.  
